Example06
=========
  Geant4 ExampleN06 adapted to Virtual Monte Carlo.

  Demonstrates:
    Physics - Cherenkov and optical photon processes

  See also description of in 
    geant4/examples/novice/N06/README

Macros:
=======

  For running example with G3:
  
  run_g3.C        - macro for running example 
  g3Config.C      - configuration macro for G3 with native geometry (default)
  g3tgeoConfig.C  - configuration macro for G3 with TGeo geometry

  For running example with G4:
  
  run_g4.C     - macro for running example 
  g4Config.C   - configuration macro
  g4config.in  - Geant4 configuration macro (called from g4Config.C)
  g4config2.in - Geant4 configuration macro for setting after initializatio

  Common macros (can be calleded by run_g3.C/run_g4.C):
  
  optPhoton.C  - test macro for polarized optical photon

To run example 
===============
  
  With G3:
  root[0] .x run_g3.C      
  
  With G3 + TGeo:
  root[0] .x run_g3.C("g3tgeoConfig.C");      
  
  With G4:
  root[0] .x run_g4.C  
